  "title": "Results are hidden when iOS keyboard is dismissed",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for participating in this project! We will try to answer as soon as possible 🙏\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug 🐛**\r\nResults are hidden when iOS keyboard is dismissed\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce 🔍**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Install Angolia in Wordpress or Shopify\r\n2. Do a search from Safari iOS\r\n3. Dismiss the keyboard\r\n\r\nA live example helps a lot!   We have a simple online template for you to use for your explanations:\r\nhttp://test.waikiki.dk (Wordpress + WooCommerce)\r\nhttps://www.blacksnow.dk (Shopify)\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior 💭**\r\nWhen I dismiss the keyboard on my iOS device, I do so to obtain more viewing space. So the expected behaviour is that the results stay put, when the keyboard is dismissed.\r\n\r\n**Screenshots 🖥**\r\n![screenrecording_07-17-2018 11-05-39](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38555816/42821401-c55863d2-89d8-11e8-8179-f82968cd8920.gif)\r\n\r\n**Environment:**\r\n - OS: iOS 11.4\r\n - Browser: Safari\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nThe issue might be due to the fact, that when you dismiss the keybord in iOS, it removes focus from the input field/search form.",
